videos.description: From behind the arc, Kansas State's Dean Wade throws the overhand pass in perfect stride to Wesley Iwundu for the alley-oop slam that has the Wildcats thinking upset over Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Long-distance alley-oop from the Octagon of Doom

videos.description: After knocking off No. 1 Oklahoma, security rushes out to keep the students from rushing the court, so the Kansas State team goes into the crowd instead.
videos.headline: When court-storming is banned after upsetting No. 1, the team goes into the crowd
